REACT_APP_API_URL=/api</pre>
    </div>
    <div class="callout warn">
      <span class="callout-icon">⚠️</span>
      <div class="callout-body"><strong>Always add .env to .gitignore.</strong> Commit a <strong>.env.example</strong> file with placeholder values instead. In production, use Docker Secrets or a vault like HashiCorp Vault / AWS Secrets Manager.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

